       <h1 class="text-sm md:text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">David Guzman</h1>
       <span class="text-sm font-normal text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 pt-1">{time}</span>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm md:text-lg font-normal py-2.5 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">I'm <span class="text-cyan-600">Front-end developer</span class=""> with over 4 years of experience as a web developer.</p>
    <span class="text-sm font-normal text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 flex justify-end">
